The '''S-AAD''' was a model of aquatic anti-air destroyer employed by the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]]. It was armed with [[Missile/Legends|missile]] launchers. It also was vulnerable to all other land and sea vehicles, making it a ship best suited for escort and base defense duties.

